| 2 | `automation_runner.py` | Remove `flash_mode` and `tools` from `Agent()` kwargs | 🔴 Critical |
| 3 | `chat.py` | Fix `Browser(headless=...)` to use `BrowserConfig` | 🔴 Critical |
| 4 | `server.py` | Guard `SIGTERM` handler with platform check for Windows | 🟡 Medium |
